         <div xml:id="alalal-d42497"><!-- l2d11a6 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-d42497-Hd1e99">Articulus 6</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-d42497-Hd1e101" type="question-title">Utrum homo habuisset Angelum 
custodem si non cecidisset ?</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e104">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="69"/>ARTICULUS VI,.
<lb ed="#Bc" n="70"/>Utrum homo habuisset Angelum 
custo<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="71"/>dem si non cecidisset ?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e113">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="72"/>Sexto queritur, Utrum homo 
habuis<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="73"/>set Angelum custodem si non 
cecidis<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="74"/>set?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e122">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="75"/>Videtur autem, quod non: quia
<lb ed="#Bc" n="76"/>1. Non fuisset inclinans 
ad_pecca<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="77"/>tum: ergo non indiguisset confortante
<lb ed="#Bc" n="78"/>in bono.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e134">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="79"/>2. Item, Homo fuisset confirmatus si
<lb ed="#Bc" n="80"/>stetisset, sicut et Angelus stans: ergo
<lb ed="#Bc" n="81"/>non indiguisset tunc Angelo custode. â€”
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e143">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="82"/>3. Item, Propter corpus non indiguit,
<lb ed="#Bc" n="83"/>quia non potuit mori nisi peccaret: ergo
<lb ed="#Bc" n="84"/>nullo modo indiguit, ut videtur.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="85"/>Sep contra: Constat quod Angelum gf
<lb ed="#Bc" n="86"/>malum habuit exercitatorem : ergo et
<lb ed="#Bc" n="87"/>bonum debuit habere custodem.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e161">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="88"/>Sorvutio. Dicendum, quod habuit Aw 4
<lb ed="#Bc" n="89"/>gelum bonum custodem in primo statu.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e168">
               <pb ed="#Bc" n="225"/>
               <cb ed="#Bc" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="1"/>Ad prima autem objecta est una 
solu<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="2"/>tio, quod custodia magis est medicina |
<lb ed="#Bc" n="3"/>preservativa quam sanativa: et ideo 
ope<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="4"/>rabatur Angelus ad hoc quod 1 non 
cade<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="5"/>ret homo.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e186">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="6"/>Ap Atiup dicendum, quod post 
confir<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="7"/>mationem non habuisset custodientem -
<lb ed="#Bc" n="8"/>Angelum.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d42497-d1e196">
               <cb ed="#Bc" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="9"/>Sed utrum adhuc per Angelum in
<lb ed="#Bc" n="10"/>statu animalis corporis accepisset 
illumi<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="11"/>nationes, donec transferretur. in. 
paradi<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="12"/>sum Angelorum, et corpus vestiretur
<lb ed="#Bc" n="13"/>claritate ccelesti, non determino: sed 
be<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="14"/>ne videtur mihi hos probabilius, quam
<lb ed="#Bc" n="15"/>oppositum.
</p>
